Sentencas: A comprehensive two-dimensional model has been developed to investigate the performance of tubular solid oxide fuel cell (T-SOFC) stack with different supported structures.
Titulo: Effects of the different Supported Structures on Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performance

Sentencas: The discrepancy between the anode-supported tubular SOFC (AST-SOFC) stack and the cathode-supported tubular SOFC (CST-SOFC) stack are examined by varying temperature, electrical conductivity, porosity, contact resistance and output voltage.
Titulo: Effects of the different Supported Structures on Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performance

Sentencas: The results illustrate that the different supported structures have an significant influence on the performance of stack.
Titulo: Effects of the different Supported Structures on Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performance

Sentencas: The performance of CST-SOFC stack is much better than AST-SOFC stack for any aforementioned working parameters.
Titulo: Effects of the different Supported Structures on Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performance

Sentencas: Especially in lower temperature, smaller cathode conductivity, larger cathode porosity and lower output voltage, the advantage is more outstanding.
Titulo: Effects of the different Supported Structures on Tubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Performance
